---
layout: base.njk
title: "Easton Chop Up! | The Groove Library"
description: >
  <p><a href="https://www.mixcloud.com/legendarymusic/playlists/easton-chop-up/" target="_blank">Easton Chop Up</a> began as a love letter to music from and inspired by Africa, rooted in the vibrant, multicultural energy of Easton, Bristol. For over a decade, it lived as a mix series, an occasional club night, and a home for deep musical exploration — from Disco and Afro-funk to jazz, dub, electronic mutations and beyond.</p>

  <p>What started as local quickly found a wider audience. Easton Chop Up became a space for late-night listeners and open-minded dancers and built on curiosity rather than trends. It championed both the roots and the forward motion of global sound, always with respect for tradition and a hunger for discovery.</p>

  <p>As I have now relocated beyond Bristol, Easton Chop Up transitions into its next chapter under a new name: The Groove Library — expanding its scope from Africa-centred inspiration to a truly global musical archive, while carrying forward the same values of depth, warmth, movement and cultural dialogue.</p>

  <p>This page stands as the archive and the foundation of that journey.</p>
playlist: "easton-chop-up"
---

{# Hero Section #}
<section class="hero hero--easton region region--lg" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--xl text-center">
      <div class="hero__eyebrow hero__eyebrow--pill text-sm text-uppercase">
        Bristol · Afro-centric archive · 10+ years
      </div>

      <div class="flow flow--md">
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="hero__title">
          Easton Chop Up!
        </h1>
        <p class="hero__tagline text-xl mx-auto">
          A decade of Afro-centric digging from Bristol to the world.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__stamp" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="hero__stamp-inner">
          Easton · Bristol
        </span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


{# Description Section #}
{% if description %}
<section class="region region--lg" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow flow">
      {{ description | safe }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{# Mix Collection Section #}
<section class="region region--xl" aria-labelledby="mixes-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flow flow--xl">
      {# Section Header #}
      <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
        <h2 id="mixes-heading" class="text-3xl">
          The Archive
        </h2>

        {% if eastonChopUp.count > 0 %}
          <div class="cluster cluster--sm justify-center">
            <span class="badge">
              <wa-icon name="record-vinyl" size="sm" aria-hidden="true"></wa-icon>
              {{ eastonChopUp.count }} mixes in this collection
            </span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      {# Mix Grid #}
      {% if eastonChopUp.cloudcasts.length > 0 %}
        <div class="grid grid--2" role="list" aria-label="Easton Chop Up mixes">
          {% for mix in eastonChopUp.cloudcasts %}
            <div role="listitem">
              {% include "mix-player.njk" %}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% elif eastonChopUp.error %}
        {# Error State #}
        <div class="error" role="alert">
          <h3 class="error__title">
            <wa-icon name="triangle-exclamation" aria-hidden="true"></wa-icon>
            Unable to load mixes
          </h3>
          <p>We encountered an error while fetching the music collection. Please try again later.</p>
          <details class="my-md">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-semibold">Technical details</summary>
            <p class="text-sm my-sm"><code>{{ eastonChopUp.error }}</code></p>
          </details>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        {# Empty State #}
        <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--lg text-center py-3xl">
          <wa-icon name="music-slash" size="4x" class="text-tertiary" aria-hidden="true"></wa-icon>
          <div class="flow flow--sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl">No mixes available</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary">Check back soon for new content!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
